## 💰 Pricing Plans

TaskFlow offers flexible pricing to suit teams of all sizes:

| Plan | Price | Features |
|------|-------|----------|
| **Starter** | **Free** | • Up to 5 tasks per month<br>• Email login<br>• Basic task management<br>• Single user |
| **Professional** | **$19/user/month** | • Unlimited tasks<br>• Google OAuth integration<br>• Analytics & reporting<br>• Team collaboration<br>• Priority support |
| **Enterprise** | **$49/user/month** | • Everything in Professional<br>• Custom branding<br>• Advanced permissions<br>• API access<br>• Dedicated support<br>• SLA guarantee |

> 💡 **Note**: This is a simulated SaaS pricing model for demonstration purposes.

